wiki.summary: In “Contra”, Logic talks about how he is recently starting to blow up and go mainstream. He notices that many of these new fans were not here in the beginning, and how many of them are showing up now that he has released many successful mixtapes and albums. Similar to “Super Mario World” on "Bobby Tarantino", "Contra" is actually the name of a classic video game from the late 1980s. It was released on NES, and was a “run and gun” style video game. Read more on Last.fm.
